{"tid":22923,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[勞力士] 綠針同藍針點揀","createTime":"2016-12-04T16:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T04:07:46.000Z","uid":10533,"like":17,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3270ffb8dc34c8f9498b2540a2cb51cd5786bfd9","tid":22923,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"應該都係會買呢兩隻其中一隻<br />\n兩隻個款都鍾意 <br />\n但係有幾點令我好糾結<br />\n綠針抵玩啲 長青 但係公廁<br />\n藍針 相對唔抵玩 無咁公廁 而且新款啲 (個人其實偏好藍針)<br />\n但係問題黎啦 去親間間AD兩隻都唔會有貨 <br />\n無得拎上手試又點做決定？？<br />\n想睇下咁多位巴打對呢兩隻錶有咩評價<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0H8jgp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0H8jgp.jpg&h=b3bb98e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/001915_477bd522d16bf683390a8863acbd8d94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F001915_477bd522d16bf683390a8863acbd8d94.jpg&h=d4b89864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好啦咁如果真係決定左 可以去邊到買呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 周圍都無貨 仲要無折 如果綠針可以係55k以內 藍針可以65k以內咁就最好<br />\n有無巴打可以教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 20頭男仔 非炫富 靠自己錢買但係真係揀唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n綠針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n藍針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b8dcfb07cf79252260cadca0fabf6cefa0b3da","tid":22923,"uid":7820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"炫乜富呀大陸仔 哂命呀"},{"pid":"55a19623d2c054ac4f46576ca9076175835c86b1","tid":22923,"uid":15771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"綠針 公廁但長青 有機9折或以下<br />\n藍針 mk 唔會興好耐 多數95折<br />\n<br />\n兩隻肯排隊就一定有"},{"pid":"24b7f31ac1e